# SmartShop — Cursor Agent Configuration

## Product Vision
See docs/product-vision.md for the full product vision statement, How Might We statement, and Problem Framing Canvas insights.

## Project Summary
SmartShop is an app that compares grocery prices across nearby stores and factors in travel distance, helping budget-conscious shoppers find the best overall deal. The core AI capability uses text/image recognition to match equivalent items across stores and retrieve pricing data.

